      "text": "3. Rear seat belt buckle removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "810_3.0_jpn_11370760_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the rear seat center pivot cover A (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "810_3.0_jpn_11390235_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Disconnect the harness clip (A) and coupler (B), and remove the rear seat belt buckle (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "810_3.0_jpn_11390236_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Remove the harness clip (A) and coupler clip (B) and remove the rear seat belt buckle (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Installation Precautions"
